cu.explanation_en: AMF IP address changed to 10.0.0.1, which is unreachable and causes NG interface connection failures.

du.explanation_en: Setting tracking_area_code to -1, which is out of the valid range (typically 0 or positive), causing invalid TAC configuration.
du.explanation_zh: 将 tracking_area_code 设置为 -1，这超出了有效范围（通常为 0 或正数），导致无效的 TAC 配置。
